sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Expéditeur
    participant WS as WebSocket /ws
    participant CC as ChatController
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Destinataire

    S->>WS: CONNECT + JWT Bearer
    R->>WS: CONNECT + JWT Bearer
    S->>WS: SEND /app/chat
    WS->>CC: processMessage()
    CC->>DB: save ChatMessage
    CC->>WS: convertAndSendToUser
    WS->>R: /user/queue/messages
